1
00:00:09,750 --> 00:00:13,210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I want it to consume me. Here and now.</font>

2
00:00:15,900 --> 00:00:20,130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I want it to consume me. Here and now...</font>

3
00:00:41,740 --> 00:00:42,670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Uh-huh.</font>

4
00:00:44,410 --> 00:00:46,320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yeah, that's right.</font>

5
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:48,690
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#8a807d"><font size="8">(Merchant Copy)





<font size="12">Item Reservation Form</font></font></font></font></b></font>

6
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:48,690
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"></font></b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#bdbab9">Botan Kamiina</font></font></font>

7
00:00:46,830 --> 00:00:48,350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Those earrings...</font>

8
00:00:48,690 --> 00:00:51,580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Looks like one of our staff 
sold them off by mistake.</font>

9
00:00:52,290 --> 00:00:53,410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yeah.</font>

10
00:00:55,150 --> 00:00:57,200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I just found out myself.</font>

11
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'm so sorry.</i></font>

12
00:00:59,730 --> 00:01:01,590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I did my best to warn them.</i></font>

13
00:01:02,850 --> 00:01:08,710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>We get online orders from overseas too,
so our popular items go out of stock fast.</i></font>

14
00:01:11,430 --> 00:01:13,400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So cute!</font>

15
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:13,400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}So cute!</font>

16
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Aren't they, though?</font>

17
00:01:14,810 --> 00:01:16,090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Miss RA.</font>

18
00:01:16,090 --> 00:01:19,370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why don't we get our ears 
pierced together and wear these?</font>

19
00:01:19,370 --> 00:01:20,620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Then we'll match.</font>

20
00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:22,620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Should I hold on to these earrings, then?</font>

21
00:01:22,620 --> 00:01:23,350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes!</font>

22
00:01:25,260 --> 00:01:26,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I understand.</font>

23
00:01:29,470 --> 00:01:33,550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thank you for letting me know.</font>

24
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:49,590
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24" color="#0e0c0d"><b>{\an8}Botan Kamiina Fully Blossoms When Drunk</b></font>

