<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And you?</font>

342
00:22:41,340 --> 00:22:42,420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Same here.</font>

343
00:22:43,130 --> 00:22:46,220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Six weeks for the starter earring...</font>

344
00:22:46,220 --> 00:22:47,970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I said I'm sorry.</font>

345
00:22:47,970 --> 00:22:50,470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We can change them out together 
when the time comes.</font>

346
00:22:50,470 --> 00:22:51,520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yeah.</font>

347
00:22:51,520 --> 00:22:52,810
